Package bus

Class Vehicle

java.lang.Object
bus.Vehicle
All Implemented Interfaces:
IMileAgeEfficiency, Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
ElectricVehicle, GasVehicle
public abstract class Vehicle extends Object implements IMileAgeEfficiency, Serializable
Represents a vehicle in the vehicles' fleet factory. A vehicle has a serial number, a made, a model, a date of manufacture, a trip counter and a type.
Version:
2021-12-14
Author:
Lilas Guan
